      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. PERFECT SUNSET finished 2.5L away in fourth last time attempting 1200m at Antalya nine days ago. Reunites with Yigitcan Gokce here. Almost always in the frame and is a must for the shortlist. 1. OBRADA placed last two starts including when second last time over course and distance. This veteran of the party with thirty one victories to his name warrants respect. 3. BOCCE proved too strong two runs ago here trying 1600m. Couldn't follow up when 5.5L third last time. Finds easier assignment so rates a major player. 6. MUCHACHO maintains a good track and trip record including four wins. Continues a long winning drought. Each way hope.\",\"runners\":[2,1,3,6],\"exclusive\":false}",
